location.fullValue: FLORA Plan, Oaks at Cedar Grove

data.description: Welcome home to this lovely and well maintained 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in Fairburn in the beautiful Lakes at Cedar Grove community. This home offers a open floor plan that seamlessly connects the great room to the dining area and kitchen with a spacious Master Suite. The Lakes at Cedar Grove community offers many amenities like five lakes for fishing, a clubhouse, a swimming pool, tennis courts, and a playground. This community is conveniently located to Atlanta Shopping and Hartsfield Atlanta Airport.
